Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.94,0:00:12.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让开让开
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.64,0:00:16.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别闪开啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.25,0:00:19.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 鲁涅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.82,0:00:22.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等吉泽姐姐回来了我可要告你状哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.94,0:00:24.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可要告你状哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.18,0:00:30.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真无聊…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.13,0:00:33.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法姆她们 赶紧回来啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.03,0:00:38.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐她们回来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.29,0:00:38.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.57,0:00:41.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.56,0:00:45.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为法姆姐和吉泽姐有风的保佑嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.48,0:00:58.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,福库斯 福路利希 坠落了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.61,0:01:04.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还剩几艘
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.00,0:01:06.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,残存25艘
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.72,0:01:07.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全舰跟上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.28,0:01:10.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决不能让Grand Exile被击落
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.96,0:01:14.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西尔维厄斯脱离舰队
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.63,0:01:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Vanship队如何
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.92,0:01:17.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已全部确认离舰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.36,0:01:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没功夫去救西尔维厄斯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.97,0:01:24.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本舰队要全力在Grand Exile内部瓦解其主炮
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.96,0:01:25.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全舰跟上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.88,0:01:34.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突击部队有报告吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.91,0:01:36.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与敌方星型机发生交战
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.65,0:01:37.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后联系便中断了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.93,0:01:41.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法姆 吉泽尔…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.08,0:01:50.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.61,0:01:51.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一路辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.96,0:01:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把萨拉怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.61,0:02:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她有些累了 我让她休息一会
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.67,0:02:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点危险都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.27,0:02:05.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亏你能说出这些话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.00,0:02:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法姆…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.86,0:02:11.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萨拉陛下醒来的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.75,0:02:14.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个世界将会改变
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.17,0:02:18.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那才不是萨拉期盼的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.50,0:02:23.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用这种破坏一切的船
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.08,0:02:25.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让大家饱受痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.85,0:02:31.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这群傻鸭子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.62,0:02:34.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海涅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.42,0:02:35.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 我很安全
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.08,0:02:37.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引擎 燃料表也没有异常
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.01,0:02:38.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.61,0:02:44.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要小瞧空族魂哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.80,0:02:55.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没完没了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.94,0:02:56.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队形别乱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.58,0:02:59.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要确保法姆机的退路
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.24,0:03:07.99,gra,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法姆… 还没好吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.67,0:03:19.67,gra,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.42,0:03:23.26,gra,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会保护你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.19,0:03:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不能死
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.46,0:03:30.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁都不能死
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.96,0:03:35.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这艘船并非为破坏而生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.03,0:03:40.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它曾是以天际翱翔为目标的船
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.87,0:03:41.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天际
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.64,0:03:45.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在极荒之时
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.97,0:03:49.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们归还民的祖先造出了Exile
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.30,0:03:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从这颗星球逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.70,0:03:58.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留在这颗被他们抛弃的走向毁灭的星球的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.10,0:04:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一个梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.88,0:04:05.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超越即将毁灭的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.14,0:04:08.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自由翱翔于天际的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.88,0:04:10.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超越Exile的Exile
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.35,0:04:14.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凝聚几世代的岁月
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.34,0:04:19.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们继承了这个梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.68,0:04:28.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个梦想真的实现了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.20,0:04:36.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这艘船并未完成
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.85,0:04:39.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从很早以前就被抛弃了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.16,0:04:44.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就造了一半 就被忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.02,0:04:45.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.91,0:04:50.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我要实现这个梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.66,0:04:53.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标只有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.92,0:04:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在总帅萨拉的麾下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.97,0:04:58.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,统一世界 走向和平
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.01,0:05:02.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为达目的 不择手段
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.09,0:05:16.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在Grand Exile内部再次听到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.72,0:05:18.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,推定10度以上的供弹仓运转音
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.37,0:05:21.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标方位191度
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.40,0:05:22.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标并未改变
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.24,0:05:26.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何都要干掉图兰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.88,0:05:27.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真头疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.67,0:05:30.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是西尔维厄斯又动弹不得
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.51,0:05:34.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全员做好冲击准备
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.54,0:05:36.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发射舰首长管炮的同时
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.76,0:05:37.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全速后退
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.43,0:05:38.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发射
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.17,0:05:45.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前方主炮 可以使用
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.11,0:05:47.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左右主炮 可以使用
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.84,0:05:48.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.97,0:05:51.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以最大船速 与本队汇合
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.78,0:05:54.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标是破坏Grand Exile的主炮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.73,0:06:04.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路斯吉尼亚阁下带来Grand Exile的同时也带来了和平
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.49,0:06:07.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们来为其奠基吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.94,0:06:09.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,荣光同在 奥古斯塔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.28,0:06:14.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实阁下的做法是最快的捷径
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.84,0:06:19.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是嘛 反正我也还乳臭未干
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.51,0:06:22.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引擎动力下降
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.95,0:06:24.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,B群炮塔消失
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.73,0:06:26.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三第四战队脱离
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.91,0:06:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法维持阵形
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.63,0:06:30.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剥夺自由与意志
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.81,0:06:33.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只剩一口气的活着有什么意义
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.48,0:06:36.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了实现奥古斯塔萨拉的梦想与理想
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.18,0:06:37.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要放弃！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.47,0:06:39.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全军突击
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.98,0:06:41.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,荣光同在 奥古斯塔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.72,0:06:43.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,荣光同在 奥古斯塔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.24,0:06:46.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Grand Race这理想确实很伟大
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.64,0:06:50.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 你也应该深知
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.99,0:06:55.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是法拉芙娜兹陛下都没做到的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.74,0:06:58.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只凭着理想 世界不会改变
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.18,0:07:00.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.24,0:07:02.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.04,0:07:04.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「这就是现实」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.19,0:07:07.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「没那么简单」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.67,0:07:10.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「只凭理想的冲劲」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.07,0:07:13.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「净是力不能及的事」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.55,0:07:16.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.75,0:07:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.68,0:07:27.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是想做梦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.03,0:07:30.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.20,0:07:33.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Grand Race指引我至今
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.11,0:07:39.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全凭这份思念 让我一直在天空翱翔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.31,0:07:42.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这是那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.22,0:07:47.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实现Grand Race的人们给我的珍贵梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.44,0:07:56.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我也会接着飞下去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.86,0:08:14.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,定时鱼雷 发射
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.20,0:08:19.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以我舰做盾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.04,0:08:22.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为我们的皇帝开出一条路
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.79,0:08:25.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全炮门 集中在准备中的敌主炮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.75,0:08:32.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那果然不是攻击兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.17,0:08:33.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而更像是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.25,0:08:38.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办 暂时撤退也是选项之一
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.43,0:08:42.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法姆一定会把萨拉带回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.29,0:08:49.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全炮门 瞄准Grand Exile内壁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.45,0:08:51.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我舰吸引触手的注意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.77,0:08:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开火
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.13,0:09:05.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如你所说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.22,0:09:09.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的梦想可能又会破灭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.89,0:09:18.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家的仇恨 悲伤可能并不会消失
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.32,0:09:25.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我还是想飞下去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.39,0:09:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为一定会有人因梦想而联系起来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.61,0:10:03.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们来了真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.72,0:10:09.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能带萨拉陛下走
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.09,0:10:17.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.23,0:10:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌外部装甲发出异常的破坏声
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.57,0:10:40.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,临界状态也在主炮附近
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.60,0:10:41.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.77,0:10:44.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,构造全体正在急速扩大
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.03,0:10:55.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那果然不是主炮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.07,0:10:57.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是巨大的推进器
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.57,0:11:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.14,0:11:06.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本想把大家带到天上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.01,0:11:10.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以准备了许多翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.16,0:11:13.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但却还是未能实现
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.74,0:11:17.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.34,0:11:19.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这艘傻鸭子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.97,0:11:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能打下去了 跟上我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.88,0:11:47.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Grand Exile的构造部分 25… 28%损坏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.93,0:11:49.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自毁速度正在加快
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.33,0:11:51.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各舰请求下令
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.16,0:11:56.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全员 准备退舰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.75,0:12:00.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的时代结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.18,0:12:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全员 解除武装后 听从联合军的指示
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.63,0:12:06.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但… 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.99,0:12:11.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是总统阁下事先下的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.42,0:12:18.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸠泽尔 可以拜托你件事情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.33,0:12:18.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.66,0:12:26.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把这个交给我的孙女
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.18,0:12:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你… 从一开始就知道会这样？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.81,0:12:52.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明知如此还要这样？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.76,0:12:57.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路斯吉尼亚 你也…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.44,0:13:00.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萨拉她…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.69,0:13:03.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萨拉她不想再让任何人死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.89,0:13:18.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉安娜说并没因生为钥匙而感到不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.52,0:13:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚劳达和我也是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.48,0:13:23.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萨拉陛下就拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.33,0:13:25.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路斯吉尼亚！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.29,0:13:25.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法姆！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.33,0:13:27.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你杀了这么多人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.13,0:13:29.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让这么多人伤心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.32,0:13:32.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是男子汉就承担起责任啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.31,0:13:34.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路斯吉尼亚！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.74,0:13:38.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回去吧 法姆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.44,0:13:48.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为脱落物龙骨已超重70%了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.39,0:13:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船已经撑不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.66,0:13:51.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突击部队呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.82,0:13:54.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有联系说各自开始逃脱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.10,0:13:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萨拉呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.41,0:13:58.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没收到接收奥古斯塔的报告
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.29,0:14:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法姆…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.28,0:14:07.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Grand Exile下坠
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.41,0:14:10.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,升限坠至安全域还有150秒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.19,0:14:16.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞纳帕迪舰…！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.26,0:14:16.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.92,0:14:21.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我走 奥兰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.81,0:14:22.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索鲁修
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.82,0:14:25.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全军 跟随塞纳帕迪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.83,0:14:26.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始脱离
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.09,0:14:44.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放弃收回奥古斯塔救出部队
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.69,0:14:48.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动力全开 脱离Grand Exile
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.68,0:14:50.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米莉亚…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.65,0:14:53.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动力全开 上浮！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.31,0:15:05.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前进10秒 右上方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.89,0:15:07.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.39,0:15:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉安娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.45,0:15:44.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个世界 真的会…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.32,0:15:47.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改变… 吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.59,0:16:31.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法姆…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.32,0:16:40.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个引擎声
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.92,0:16:41.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是法姆机！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.17,0:16:50.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Vespa传来发光信号
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.92,0:16:53.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等成功救出奥古斯塔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.86,0:16:57.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法姆… 吉泽尔…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.57,0:16:59.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也很努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.20,0:17:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥古斯塔平安无恙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.23,0:17:10.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥古斯塔… 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.24,0:17:12.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得好啊你这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.77,0:17:13.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻鸭子！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.06,0:17:16.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法姆！ 吉泽！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.00,0:17:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第十六头鲸 可真是个大家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.20,0:17:21.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.80,0:17:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法姆 吉泽尔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.48,0:17:28.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萨拉 萨拉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.39,0:17:32.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萨拉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.35,0:17:34.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉泽尔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.75,0:17:37.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法姆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.15,0:17:38.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萨拉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.74,0:17:42.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瓦桑特呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.95,0:17:43.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路斯吉尼亚呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.94,0:17:44.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们二人在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.25,0:17:47.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法姆 他们俩呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.29,0:17:49.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法姆！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.34,0:18:21.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的就这些吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.51,0:18:23.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他没有藏起来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.87,0:18:25.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这是怀疑我们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.68,0:18:28.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿德斯完全同意解除武装
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.62,0:18:32.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是用高级克劳迪亚单元做的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.44,0:18:33.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能卖个好价钱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.94,0:18:36.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们也不要发呆了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.41,0:18:37.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干活啦 干活！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.06,0:18:41.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用这个单元能做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.62,0:18:44.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说图兰开始开发新的发电机了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.16,0:18:48.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在此手捧从Grand Lake的水源——
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.34,0:18:54.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Hole的碧蓝深潭里涌出的神圣之水
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.27,0:19:03.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来拿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.56,0:19:09.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以此为契机 加盟的各国作为友好邻国共存
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.04,0:19:13.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽力维持和平与安全
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.28,0:19:18.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来世界终于可以向前进了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.33,0:19:21.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 大家一起加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.40,0:19:26.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿德斯还有很多人心有不安
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.81,0:19:29.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥兰 要帮助大家哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.08,0:19:31.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,荣光同在 奥古斯塔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.76,0:19:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有奥兰阁下来做善后工作
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.57,0:19:37.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们心里也很有底
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.91,0:19:40.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来前任是索鲁修
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.11,0:19:42.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.33,0:19:51.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也能学会驾驶Vespa吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.23,0:19:55.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得如何 瓦桑特？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.54,0:20:01.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把这个交给你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.55,0:20:02.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.16,0:20:07.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和法姆一模一样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.28,0:20:08.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.35,0:20:10.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萨德里元帅说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.86,0:20:12.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「把这个交给我孙女」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.24,0:20:15.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.35,0:20:21.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,踩了他好多好多脚啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.16,0:20:21.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法姆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.84,0:20:22.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了法姆姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.14,0:20:24.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许哭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.74,0:20:27.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想跟他说好多话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.17,0:20:30.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问问母亲的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.89,0:20:34.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想让他吃好多土豆面包啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.64,0:20:52.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路斯吉尼亚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.74,0:20:56.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的对姐姐大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.99,0:21:19.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.87,0:21:21.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在干什么 迪安
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.56,0:21:22.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法姆？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.73,0:21:24.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪安不参加的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.14,0:21:25.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就算赢了也没什么值得骄傲的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.17,0:21:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 快点去准备
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.05,0:21:29.93,gra,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等 等等 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.93,0:21:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.10,0:21:33.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果没有飞艇 可以把我们的借给你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.33,0:21:34.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会驾驶的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.67,0:21:37.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽情享受劲风
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.69,0:21:38.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劲风
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.92,0:21:40.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也不会输的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.78,0:21:43.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Grand Race 一起飞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.43,0:21:44.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法姆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.49,0:21:47.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳斯 拉薇
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.53,0:21:48.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾尔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.93,0:21:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有趣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.49,0:21:54.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起飞嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.42,0:21:55.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快松开
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.63,0:21:56.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法姆！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.33,0:22:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还能再飞吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.52,0:22:03.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英麦曼…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.14,0:22:05.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然能飞啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.10,0:22:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.21,0:22:08.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到时候咱们三个一起飞
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.74,0:22:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 迪奥？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.95,0:22:12.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.68,0:22:16.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法姆 吉泽尔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.66,0:22:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.15,0:22:19.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米莉亚公主
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.32,0:22:23.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米莉亚 好好看着
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.27,0:22:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会赢的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.52,0:22:27.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赢？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.79,0:22:30.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪安
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.85,0:22:32.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别看这边
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.75,0:22:37.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 露西奥拉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.56,0:22:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 接下来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.71,0:22:52.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二届Grand Race正式开始
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.14,0:23:03.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全世界的各位
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.47,0:23:07.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再次迎来的这让人愉悦的一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.34,0:23:09.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们一起庆祝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
